Matthew McGrory https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matthew_McGrory 0 Matthew McGrory (May 17, 1973 – August 8, 2005) was an American actor, known for his great height. He held the Guiness World Records title for tallest actor, biggest feet and longest toe. Matthew_McGrory ( May_17_,_1973 – August_8_,_2005 ) was an_American_actor , known for his_great_height . He held the_Guiness_World_Records_title for tallest_actor , biggest_feet_and_longest_toe .
